name: comfortable and cozy
ISD_address: 4 Peter Parley RD 11 1 Jamaica Plain MA 02130
neighborhood_overview:
The house is located in a very diverse neighborhood with many different great venues from cafes and casual/ formal / ethnic / vegan / fast casual and Samuel Adams brewery within 10 to 15 min walking distance.
People enjoy the proximity to downtown in a very bike friendly neighborhood. (15 min by bike or 12 min by train.
Franklin Park / Zoo is two blocks away and many other parks within 20 min walking distance such as the famous Arnold Arboretum Park of Harvard university.
description:
Five minutes walking distance to subway station. A newly renovated 2 family victorian home which is located in a very diverse neighborhood where you can Walk to cafes, restaurants and parks. Neighborhood is a bike friendly and very close to Zip car. The Room, Kichen and bathroom are located on the lower level with a second and convenient access/ exit.
The room is very clean, comfortable and modern. share bath and kitchen with another Airbnb guest in case room is booked as well.

The space
There is a patio on the garden level which guest can use. There are 7 steps from the street level to the front of the house.
14 steps from main level to the lower level.
7 steps on the rear egress from lower level to the patio area in the rear of the house.

Guest access
There is a patio in the back of the house with a couple of tables and chairs that are designated for the first floor apartment, where they can smoke or grill if they want to.<
